---
---

<section id="enfoque-horizontal" data-horizontal class="relative bg-[#EEE5DB] z-20">
  <div class="sticky top-0 h-[100dvh] w-full flex flex-col overflow-hidden pt-[80px] lg:pt-[110px] pb-6">

    <div class="flex-1 w-full flex flex-col lg:flex-row relative">

      <!-- Izquierda fija -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-[35%] h-[30dvh] lg:h-full flex flex-col justify-center px-6 lg:px-16 relative z-30 pointer-events-none shrink-0">
        <div class="max-w-md w-full">
          <span class="text-forest font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-2 md:mb-4 block">La Metodología</span>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-main mb-2 md:mb-6 tracking-tight leading-[0.95]">Cómo<br class="hidden lg:block"> trabajo.</h2>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-muted font-light leading-relaxed max-w-sm hidden sm:block">
            Una orientación psicoanalítica donde la palabra tiene un lugar central y el proceso se construye a tu ritmo.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Derecha — track horizontal -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-[65%] h-[70dvh] lg:h-full relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-start lg:justify-center bg-[#EEE5DB] z-20 mt-4 lg:mt-0" id="track-container">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-12 md:w-24 lg:w-48 h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#EEE5DB] to-transparent z-30 pointer-events-none"></div>

        <div id="h-track" class="flex items-center h-full w-max px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 gap-8 md:gap-16 lg:gap-32 pb-16 lg:pb-0">

          <!-- 01 -->
          <div class="h-step-card w-[85vw] sm:w-[60vw] lg:w-[40vw] shrink-0 relative flex flex-col justify-center group">
            <div class="relative pl-6 md:pl-12 border-l border-main/20 group-hover:border-accent transition-colors duration-500">
              <div class="h-step-number absolute -left-4 md:-left-8 -top-12 md:-top-24 text-[6rem] md:text-[11rem] font-display font-bold text-main/5 leading-none tracking-tighter select-none pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">01</div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-main mb-4 md:mb-6 relative z-10">Escucha sin juicio</h3>
              <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-muted leading-relaxed font-light relative z-10">La palabra tiene un lugar central. Muchos de los malestares que vivimos no son del todo conscientes, y poder ponerlos en palabras es el primer paso para comprenderlos.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 02 -->
          <div class="h-step-card w-[85vw] sm:w-[60vw] lg:w-[40vw] shrink-0 relative flex flex-col justify-center group">
            <div class="relative pl-6 md:pl-12 border-l border-main/20 group-hover:border-accent transition-colors duration-500">
              <div class="h-step-number absolute -left-4 md:-left-8 -top-12 md:-top-24 text-[6rem] md:text-[11rem] font-display font-bold text-main/5 leading-none tracking-tighter select-none pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">02</div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-main mb-4 md:mb-6 relative z-10">Análisis</h3>
              <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-muted leading-relaxed font-light relative z-10">El trabajo no se centra solo en aliviar el malestar, sino en comprender qué lo sostiene. Los cambios más duraderos se dan cuando podemos ir más allá del síntoma y entender su sentido.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 03 -->
          <div class="h-step-card w-[85vw] sm:w-[60vw] lg:w-[40vw] shrink-0 relative flex flex-col justify-center group">
            <div class="relative pl-6 md:pl-12 border-l border-main/20 group-hover:border-accent transition-colors duration-500">
              <div class="h-step-number absolute -left-4 md:-left-8 -top-12 md:-top-24 text-[6rem] md:text-[11rem] font-display font-bold text-main/5 leading-none tracking-tighter select-none pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">03</div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-main mb-4 md:mb-6 relative z-10">Proceso</h3>
              <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-muted leading-relaxed font-light relative z-10">No hay soluciones inmediatas ni un recorrido prefijado. Cada proceso es distinto y se va construyendo con el tiempo. La terapia es un espacio donde algo puede ir tomando forma poco a poco.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 04 -->
          <div class="h-step-card w-[85vw] sm:w-[60vw] lg:w-[40vw] shrink-0 relative flex flex-col justify-center group">
            <div class="relative pl-6 md:pl-12 border-l border-main/20 group-hover:border-accent transition-colors duration-500">
              <div class="h-step-number absolute -left-4 md:-left-8 -top-12 md:-top-24 text-[6rem] md:text-[11rem] font-display font-bold text-main/5 leading-none tracking-tighter select-none pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">04</div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-main mb-4 md:mb-6 relative z-10">Autonomía</h3>
              <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-muted leading-relaxed font-light relative z-10">El objetivo no es ofrecer respuestas, sino que puedas encontrar una manera más propia de entender lo que te ocurre y posicionarte frente a ello con mayor libertad.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="w-[5vw] lg:w-[5vw] shrink-0"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Barra de progreso -->
    <div class="w-full relative z-40 shrink-0 px-6 lg:px-16 mt-auto pb-4 lg:pb-0 lg:mt-0">
      <div class="flex justify-between text-[9px] md:text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-main/40 mb-3">
        <span class="w-1/2 md:w-1/4 text-left">01. Escucha</span>
        <span class="w-1/4 text-center hidden md:block">02. Análisis</span>
        <span class="w-1/4 text-center hidden md:block">03. Proceso</span>
        <span class="w-1/2 md:w-1/4 text-right">04. Autonomía</span>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full h-[3px] bg-main/10 relative rounded-full overflow-hidden" role="progressbar" aria-label="Progreso de la metodología" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" aria-valuenow="0">
        <div id="h-progress" class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-forest/60 via-forest to-accent w-0 rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
